data.name: label1.Text
data.value: The rules: 1) Space bar is to shoot. 2) A/D and Left/right arrows move. 3) If you defeat all the aliens then you win. 4) If the aliens reach you then you lose. 5) The aliens will snake towards you. 6) High scores will be kept at the end of a game. 7) This game uses Dark Souls logic, there is no pause. 8) After everything is dead, press space again to progress to the game over screen.
